            "control-category": "access-control",
            "inherent-risk": "7.3",
            "residual-risk": "7.3",
            "maestro-layer": "L6 — Security and Compliance",
            "recommendation": "Implement defense-in-depth prompt injection detection at the Orchestrator layer, independent of Guardrails. Apply separate input classification on the Orchestrator (policy engine, second-stage classifier, or LLM-based guard). Enforce least-privilege on Guardrails→Orchestrator flows.",
            "effort-estimate": "High"
          }
        },
        {
          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/privilege-escalation",
