            "recommendation": "Output encoding and context-aware sanitization on LLM responses to User browser. Server-side: DOMPurify or sanitize-html on generated text. Response header: Content-Security-Policy with strict script-src 'self' 'nonce-<nonce>'. Client: textContent (not innerHTML); React {value} JSX (not dangerouslySetInnerHTML).",
